headline: Redburn starts Domino’s with Sell on heavy GLP-1 exposure
summary: As previously reported, Redburn Atlantic initiated coverage of Domino’s Pizza (DPZ) with a Sell rating and $340 price target Domino’s faces the heaviest pressure from GLP-1 weight loss drug adoption, with high exposure to dinner occasions and lower-income consumers, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
